sequenceDiagram
    participant Client as Browser/HTMX
    participant CF as Cloudflare
    participant N as nginx
    participant G as Gunicorn
    participant D as Django
    participant R as Redis
    participant DB as MySQL

    Client->>CF: HTTPS Request
    CF->>N: Forward (X-Forwarded-Proto=https)
    N->>G: unix socket proxy
    G->>D: WSGI

    D->>R: Get session + cache checks
    alt Cache hit for results/turnout/etc
        R-->>D: Return cached value
    else Miss
        D->>DB: ORM queries
        DB-->>D: Data
        D->>R: cache.set(...)
    end

    D-->>G: HttpResponse (full or fragment)
    G-->>N
    N-->>CF
    CF-->>Client

    Note over D,R: Brute-force, password reset state,<br/>election results & turnout are Redis-backed
